premise_source_doc_sentence: Jensen Ross Ackles  (  born March 1 , 1978  )  is an American actor and director .

He is known for his roles in television as Eric Brady in Days of Our Lives , which earned him several Daytime Emmy Award nominations , as well as Alec/X5 -494 in Dark Angel and Jason Teague in Smallville .
He also starred as the lead in the box office success My Bloody Valentine 3D and portrayed Jason Todd in the popular animated film Batman : Under the Red Hood .
Ackles currently stars as Dean Winchester on the CW series Supernatural .

The narrative follows the series ' protagonists Sam  (  Jared Padalecki  )  and Dean Winchester  (  Jensen Ackles  )  -- brothers who travel the continental United States hunting supernatural creatures -- as they attempt to save the latter 's soul from damnation .
